data.description: A NEW Price improvement! Check this one out! Move-in ready! Beautifully updated 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home with no HOA fees. Located on large corner lot with lots of parking. Newer roof, air conditioning, water heater, siding, porch, fencing and so much more including premium grade quartz countertops, cabinets, and appliances.  TVs are included. There's also newer vinyl flooring throughout. Convenient location to beaches, shopping, theaters, museums, sports complex and airport!  Come see this charming home for yourself and make it your dream home. It can also be purchased furnished.
